A documentary directed by Pascale Lamche, titled 'WINNIE'
has caused raging emotions to South African, on the role that struggle stalwart Winnie Madikizela-Mandela
played in bringing about the release of former president Nelson Mandela and democracy
in Mzansi.The documentary looks into the political life of Mam' Winnie
which includes broad unseen archival footage and interviews with her.The documentary explores and answers questions that many
